  "body": "### Description\r\nUpdated design for the chat list (left panel). Design improvements include:\r\n\r\n- A more condensed list of chats\r\n- Clearer highlight of current chat\r\n- Background color to highlight the chat area and bring focus to the conversation\r\n\r\n### Current implementation vs new design\r\n![group2](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/48223116-0a66fb00-e375-11e8-83d6-a3f28dbabd47.png)\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n\r\n- [ ] Implement chat rows\r\n- [ ] Review margins and paddings of rows\r\n- [ ] Implement row highlight\r\n- [ ] Review margins and paddings of row highlight\r\n- [ ] Implement public channel row design\r\n- [ ] Apply background color\r\n- [ ] Review font sizes, colors and weights according to the designs\r\n- [ ] Review it with your UX friend before merging :)\r\n\r\n[Designs @ Figma ](https://www.figma.com/file/MRYBI5axcTwL4Ft8xAYhFOfy/Desktop-Chat?node-id=309%3A11691)\r\n",
